---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Solutions
description: Acme Chemicals end-to-end chemical solutions — custom formulation, regulatory compliance support, supply chain management, and technical services.
permalink: /solutions/
---

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span>Solutions</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Solutions Built Around You</h1>
    <p class="lead">More than a chemical supplier — a formulation partner. We work alongside your team from initial concept through scale-up, compliance, and ongoing supply.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for solution in collections.solutions | reverse %}
      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="{{ solution.data.image }}" alt="{{ solution.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-tag">{{ solution.data.category }}</span>
          <h3>{{ solution.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ solution.data.excerpt }}</p>
          <a href="{{ solution.url }}" class="card-link">Explore Solution</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="two-col-content">
        <h2>Our solution delivery process</h2>
        <p>Every Acme Chemicals engagement begins with deep technical discovery. We don't sell products — we solve problems. Our structured approach ensures every recommendation is grounded in your specific process, regulatory environment, and performance requirements.</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>Technical needs assessment and site visit</li>
          <li>Laboratory screening and formulation development</li>
          <li>Pilot-scale validation and process optimization</li>
          <li>Regulatory documentation and compliance support</li>
          <li>Commercial scale-up and ongoing supply management</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="two-col-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576086213369-97a306d36557?w=600&h=450&fit=crop" alt="Chemical research and development laboratory" style="border-radius: 20px;">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Tell us about your challenge</h2>
    <p>Our applications team is ready to discuss your formulation goals. No commitment required — just a conversation.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Start a Conversation</a>
      <a href="/company/" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">About Our Experts</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
